@node colsh
Colour_shift
============

Colour Shifter was written to change the colours on the default screen to be
BBS complient.  Try it on workbench, it's wierd..

Installation: 	Bung it where you like, preferably in the command path.

Usage:		Type 'colour_shift'

Getting rid of it:
		copy envarc:sys/palette.prefs env:sys
@endnode
@node help
Help ?
======

My screen has gone all funny colours, and I can't get them back..

Getting rid of it:
		copy envarc:sys/palette.prefs env:sys

(errrm, thats all the help for today kiddies)
@endnode
